              Sent To Email</label></div>

          <div class="relative mx-3 mt-6 h-10 w-full min-w-[200px]"><input
              class="text-blue-gray-700 disabled:bg-blue-gray-50 placeholder-shown:border-blue-gray-200 placeholder-shown:border-t-blue-gray-200 border-blue-gray-200 peer h-full w-full rounded-[7px] border border-t-transparent bg-transparent px-3 py-2.5 font-sans text-sm font-normal outline outline-0 transition-all placeholder-shown:border focus:border-2 focus:border-gray-900 focus:border-t-transparent focus:outline-0 disabled:border-0"
              placeholder="   " /><label
